    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly spectacular shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it left the showroom. I've babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it\u2019s always sparkling. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is your lucky day. Drop me a message and come fall in love with your new ride! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
