      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a benchmark of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for optimized torque across the rev range. This example is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, driving power through a GKN-sourced M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless, with documented reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. Suspension geometry is true, utilizing the original aluminum control arms and specific M-tuned damping. Maintenance is exhaustive, including a recent valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing service, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with mechanical symphony. An unmolested, investment-grade driver's car.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service history. No cosmetic or mechanical defects. Garage kept. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a private collection. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free of even the smallest stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, and the dashboard remains pristine under a dedicated UV-protective coating. Every electronic component, from the adaptive cruise control to the high-fidelity sound system, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive folder of maintenance documentation included. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
